    "title": "Life Generations Healthcare: Unauthorized Email Access Exposes Patient Data at 29 California Facilities",
    "summary": "An unauthorized party accessed multiple employee email accounts at Life Generations Healthcare LLC (LGH), a Santa Ana, California-based multi-facility healthcare operator, between May 24 and June 12, 2023. LGH operates 29 skilled nursing and behavioral health facilities in California and one in Nevada. The breach compromised names, addresses, dates of birth, medical information, health insurance details, Social Security numbers, driver's license numbers, and financial account information for approximately 5,800 individuals. LGH notified the California Attorney General on November 3, 2023.",
