    "title": "Medical Management Resource Group / American Vision Partners: Hacking Incident Affects 2.35 Million Patients",
    "summary": "On November 14, 2023, Medical Management Resource Group LLC (MMRG), doing business as American Vision Partners — which provides administrative support to ophthalmology practices across Arizona, California, Nevada, New Mexico, and Texas — detected unauthorized activity on its network. A forensic investigation confirmed that by December 6, 2023, an unauthorized party had accessed and removed files containing protected health information of 2,350,236 individuals. Exposed data included names, contact details, dates of birth, medical service and prescription records, and for some patients, Social Security numbers and health insurance information. Multiple class action lawsuits were filed in the District of Arizona.",
