    "enriched_summary": "On November 14, 2023, Medical Management Resource Group LLC (operating as American Vision Partners), which provides administrative support to ophthalmology practices across five states, detected unauthorized activity on its network. Investigation determined that by around December 6, 2023, an unauthorized party had accessed and removed files containing protected health information for over 2.35 million patients. MMRG promptly isolated affected systems and engaged outside cybersecurity firms, but the breadth of the exfiltration — covering patients of multiple affiliated eye care practices — triggered three separate class action lawsuits within days of the February 2024 notification.",
