    "title": "Covenant Care California: Unauthorized Network Access Exposes Patient and Employee Data",
    "summary": "Covenant Care California, LLC — a provider of skilled nursing, rehabilitation, and home health services operating under brands including Focus Health, Elevate Home Health, Choice Home Health Care, and San Diego Home Health — experienced an unauthorized network intrusion between November 12-14, 2023. An unauthorized party accessed and copied files containing patient names, dates of birth, Social Security numbers, financial account numbers, medical information, health insurance details, and driver's license numbers. Notification letters were sent to affected individuals on August 29, 2024 — approximately nine months after discovery — and class action investigations were launched by multiple law firms.",
