    "industry": "Healthcare",
    "featured": false,
    "enriched_summary": "Between November 12-14, 2023, an unauthorized actor gained access to Covenant Care California's network and copied files containing sensitive patient and employee data. Covenant Care operates skilled nursing, rehabilitation, and home health services under multiple brand names including Focus Health, Elevate Home Health, Choice Home Health Care, and San Diego Home Health. Despite discovering the breach in November 2023, notification letters were not sent to affected individuals until August 29, 2024 — approximately nine months later — triggering class action investigations by multiple law firms. The delayed notification amplified legal exposure for the organization.",
