    "title": "Dameron Hospital: RansomHouse attack compromises 272,475 patients, $650K settlement",
    "summary": "On approximately December 5, 2023, RansomHouse actors breached Dameron Hospital (Stockton, CA), exfiltrating over 480 GB of data including names, addresses, emails, SSNs, payment/account information, and health insurance and medical data for 272,475 individuals. Dameron disclosed the breach in early 2024 and issued notifications. The ransomware group threatened to release the data; some information was disseminated on the dark web. Dameron agreed to a $650,000 class action settlement. While the breach occurred in December 2023, patient notifications and legal proceedings were active throughout 2024.",
