      "May 2024: 3 Microsoft 365 accounts compromised via phishing, affecting 1,598 individuals",
      "September 2024: server incident affecting 2,334 individuals",
      "Data exposed: names, SSNs, DOBs, addresses, medical record numbers, phone numbers, mental health treatment records",
      "DMH disabled affected accounts and reset Microsoft 365 and MFA credentials after each incident"
