    "title": "Gardner Health Services: San Jose community health center affected by TriZetto billing vendor breach, 26,000 patients notified December 2025",
    "summary": "Gardner Health Services, a San Jose, California-based Federally Qualified Health Center providing medical, dental, substance use, and behavioral health services, was notified on December 9, 2025 that billing vendor TriZetto Provider Solutions had been breached. Unauthorized access to TriZetto's web portal began in November 2024 and was discovered October 2, 2025. Approximately 26,000 Gardner Health patients were affected; overall the TriZetto breach impacted 3.43 million individuals across multiple healthcare clients. Gardner Health mailed breach notification letters to affected patients on December 22, 2025. Exposed data included names, addresses, birthdates, Social Security numbers, and health insurance member numbers.",
