      "HNFS falsely certified NIST SP 800-53 cybersecurity compliance in annual reports to the Defense Health Agency",
      "Second major DOJ settlement under the Civil Cyber-Fraud Initiative (announced October 2021)",
      "HNFS and Centene maintained no vulnerabilities were exploited, no data breach occurred, and no servicemember data was lost",
      "Settlement covers TRICARE contract serving active duty servicemembers and their families"
