    "title": "Hims & Hers: Customer support platform breached via social engineering",
    "summary": "San Francisco-based telehealth pharmacy Hims & Hers (2.5M+ subscribers) had its Zendesk customer support platform accessed by the ShinyHunters extortion gang between February 4-7, 2026. Attackers used social engineering to compromise Okta SSO credentials and steal millions of customer support tickets containing names and contact information; medical records and provider communications were not exposed. The company notified the California Attorney General on April 2, 2026, is sending individual breach notifications, and is offering 12 months of free credit monitoring; class action investigations were launched by multiple law firms.",
